author: SomeOrdinaryGamers
description:
Hello guys and gals, it's me Mutahar again! This time we take a look at what appears to be a serious moderation problem that only gets worse by the day. YouTube has been accused of ramping up it's AI moderation and is now alleged to have been taking down channels in one of the largest ban waves we've seen. What's actually happening? Let's find out! Thanks for watching!
Like, Comment and Subscribe for more videos!
title: I Can See YouTube's Moderation Taking This Video Down...
